    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Correspondence
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Asset purchase facility (APF) ceiling, November 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The letters exchanged between the Chancellor of the Exchequer and the Governor of the Bank of England confirm the increase in the limit of assets that the APF is authorised to purchase, financed by the issuance of central bank reserves.</p>

  </div>
</div>

